Name: TYPE OF CARGO
Explanation: THE TYPE OF CARGO TO BE SUPPLIED BY THE SPECIFIC SUPPLY SHIP.

Name: TYPE OF STORES
Explanation: THE TYPE OF CARGO AVAILABLE FOR TRANSFER AS STORES.

Name: TYPE OF REPLENISHMENT CARGO
Explanation: THE TYPE OF CARGO AVAILABLE FOR REPLENISHMENT.

Name: TYPE OF CARGO REMAINING
Explanation: THE SPECIFIC TYPE(S) OF CARGO REMAINING IN A SUPPLY SHIP.

Name: TYPE OF CARGO REQUIRED
Explanation: THE TYPE(S) OF CARGO REQUIRED BY THE CUSTOMER SHIP.

Name: TYPE OF CARGO EMBARKED
Explanation: TYPE OF CARGO EMBARKED AND HAZARDS (IMO)
